I am planning on taking CS169 and EE16B Fall 2016 but they have the same lecture times.  I assumed this would be okay because I heard 169 doesn't have a final and I thought at least one of the lectures would be webcasted, but I just read on the 169 site that lecture attendance will be required.  Will EE16B have mandatory lectures as well and would taking these two classes at the same time be feasible given the conflict?
